  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_3' aria-label=\" Ramesh A. Naika versus The Registrar General, High Court of Karnataka Etc. pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('3','2025','2025_2_1721_1744','2025INSC303'); ><font size='4'> <strong>RAMESH A. NAIKA<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>THE REGISTRAR GENERAL, HIGH COURT OF KARNATAKA ETC. </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 2 S.C.R. 1721</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 303</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010003492025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : VIKRAM NATH<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, SANJAY KAROL, SANDEEP MEHTA</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Appellant-R, a bank manager, was convicted of murdering his two minor children, along with his sister-in-law and mother-in- law, in June 2010. His motive stemmed from disapproval of his sister-in-law&rsquo;s relationship, which his wife and On 16.06.2010, he allegedly killed his sister-in-law and mother-in- law at his house in Tumkur and disposed of their bodies in a sump tank. The next day, he took his children to a water tank in Mangalore and drowned them. He later sent messages to his wife, suggesting she end her life. His<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 13-02-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CRIMINAL APPEAL No. 877-878/2020</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Case Partly allowed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 3 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('3','2025','2025_2_1721_1744','2025INSC303','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('3','2025','2025_2_1721_1744','2025INSC303','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('3','2025','2025_2_1721_1744','2025INSC303');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('3','2025','2025_2_1721_1744','2025INSC303','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
